archivedCranVersions.Rd

archivedCranVersions -------------------------------------------------------- Archived CRAN versions

Usage

archivedCranVersions(package, ref_date = NULL)

Arguments

package

package name

ref_date

default: NULL

Examples

packages <- c("ggplot2", "swmmr", "kwb.hantush")
archivedCranVersions(packages)
